snippet: Prince Fielder hit two of Texas’s season-high five homers and drove in five runs as the Rangers extended their lead with a 14-3 victory over the visiting Astros.
abstract: Baseball Roundup; Texas Rangers defeat Houston Astros, 14-3; other MLB scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Prince Fielder hit two of Texas’s season-high five homers and drove in five runs as the Rangers extended their lead with a 14-3 victory over the visiting Astros.
